{"tid":2034041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過咗今個禮拜 終於明白阻住香港人抗爭嘅唔係咩國安法 而係我哋自己...","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T06:41:02.000Z","uid":132174,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cde2bbc1b6adb876b18af6d787ab150fb23cad69","tid":2034041,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:20:02.000Z","msg":"一開始吹風話BNO平權就個個諗住話要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老實講我97後得本香港passport 如果我有BNO都可能諗緊差唔多嘅嘢 <br />\n但係一路叫人唔好分化齊上齊落 一路同bno holders講有得走梗係走先 聽落去真係好諷刺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得香港人有啲似猶太人 幾聰明 識得精打細算 但係又有啲自私咁 <br />\n唔同嘅係猶太人係二戰嘅時候真係俾人種族清洗<br />\n結局就係有一半嘅人去咗美國做二等公民 而以色列就繼續窮落去<br />\n佢哋嘅結局已經冇得改寫 但係我哋仲有得撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b741d2a07b7df4edb91b9e3d06bc05b67ca4b8b2","tid":2034041,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"抵啦 冇bno <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9118c0c59309470dcee1a39c4c61218b65ff46a","tid":2034041,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b741d2a07b7df4edb91b9e3d06bc05b67ca4b8b2","tid":2034041,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:30:48.000Z","msg":"抵啦 冇bno <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"u = have?"},{"pid":"e5c14de52c2515336c5751dbd8380b6f79a3a500","tid":2034041,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9118c0c59309470dcee1a39c4c61218b65ff46a","tid":2034041,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b741d2a07b7df4edb91b9e3d06bc05b67ca4b8b2","tid":